<item>
            <title>[LU-11480] Allow executing tests in random order</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11480</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Every time the Lustre test suites are run for all automated testing, the order is fixed for the test suites and all tests in those test suites are run in sequential order. Let&#8217;s implement the ability to run the tests in each test suite in random order. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Running tests in random order will help defeat any dependencies within the test suites and will, possibly, ensure that Lustre is returned to a known good state at the end of each test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre test suites</environment>
